reviewText:
Growing up as a Child in the 80's and 90's I loved Ducktales, Tale Spin, Darkwing Duck, Bonkers and so many more.
Up until a few years ago you couldn't get this series on DVD so the only way was to get this collection of tapes which i have all of them !
Yea it's nice to go buy the whole series on DVD but look at these covers the artwork is beautiful !
So me being a VHS and Movie Collector in general had to have these !
